data.description: Presenting a contemporary home nestled in the highly coveted neighborhood of Cobbs Creek. Conveniently located within walking distance of public transportation and less than a 10-minute drive from major thoroughfares, this home offers exceptional accessibility. With over 1,500 sq ft of combined above and below grade living space, the residence accommodates an open floor plan for a spacious and airy feel. Additional features include, central A/C, an enclosed porch, a tastefully landscaped rear yard, and an outdoor deck, perfect for leisure or entertaining. The home also boasts a fully finished basement, complemented by sleek stainless-steel appliances and modern recessed lighting. The property comprises three generously sized bedrooms, with the added comfort of bathrooms on each level. Seize this extraordinary opportunity to own a piece of elegance and convenience in Cobbs Creek. As of the date of listing entry, this home qualifies for a $10,000 grant through the Pathway to Prosperity program. Inquire about program specifics, guidelines and availability with your real estate representative. Schedule your tour today!
